  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">A few</span> hutumika kuzungumzia idadi ndogo ya vitu vinavyohesabika. Kwa mfano:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We have a few tasks left to finish.</span> – Unatumia <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a few</span>, kwa sababu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tasks</span> ni nomino inayohesabika.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">To take a little time</span> znači koristiti kratak vremenski period za uraditi nešto određeno. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Time</span> je nebrojiv imenica, pa koristiš <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a little</span>, a ne <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a few</span>. Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I need a little time to review this.</span> – Unatumia <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a little</span>, kwa sababu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">time</span> ni nomino isiyohesabika.</p>\n<p>Drugi primeri upotrebe:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">A few minutes</span> – <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Minutes</span> su brojive nominale.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">A little water</span> – <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Water</span> je nebrojiv imenica.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">A few emails</span> – <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Emails</span> su imenice koje se mogu izbrojati.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">A little information</span> – <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Information</span> ni nomino isiyohesabika.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
